      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Tricky 2yo race to open proceedings. OUR BRAVE BOY (2) was well backed first up and stuck on gamely while the one behind just had the perfect drop on him. That form didn't work out all that well last week but he'll strip fitter and give a bold sight. STARS OF DOM (7) charged home here on debut in a fantastic effort to grab second. Fancy 1100m would've suited better but watch for him late. SUPERBEC (9) creates interest on debut with some handy jumpouts coming into this. She's well bred and if she can run up to her public outings here, she'll be in the mix. MBUBE (4) is another debutant that's shown enough in his public outings to suggest he can run a race on debut.",
